node.text:
Hey guys, I need your help finding people deserving of a pick me up. I’ve been blessed to have gathered up so much fishing gear over a 10 year professional career and I’ve come to realize there’s no way I could possibly use all of it. 

So I’ve gathered up at least $20,000 USD of my gear, fishing rods, reels, tackle, etc, to give away. Nominate someone you know who could use some gear and my team is going to help go through all the comments and pick people to send some stuff to. Use the hash tag #JWGrassrootsGiveback in your reply or a new post to make sure we see it! Thanks!

node.text:
Happy Easter from the Wheelers!
Dressed up as the Easter Bunny’s brother, the Easter Egg Bunny. Spread some love to our friends and the people around town.

node.title: Bassmaster Elite Series La Crosse, Wisconsin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jacob Wheeler on September 10, 2021 tagging @froggtoggsfish. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and body of water.

node.text: Reeled in a 100lbs + of smallmouth good enough for 2nd going into day 2! Got some ground to make up if I want  to win the round but it feels great already knowing we made that knockout. Day off tomorrow then back after it on Sunday! @froggtoggs

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jacob Wheeler in 9 Mile Boat Launch with @teamtoyota, and @academy. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and body of water.

node.text:
Are you watching @majorleaguefishingofficial Live?! We got a Live Camera in the boat for Day 1 of Lake Saint Clair. This place is absolutely full of big smallmouth but with our format largemouth could be very competitive… Which do you think will end up playing the most, largemouth or smallmouth? 
@academy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jacob Wheeler on September 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Officially made it to Detroit. Time to rig some tackle and get ready for The start of practice Tomorrow out on Lake St Clair. @magellanoutdoors

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jacob Wheeler on September 05, 2021 tagging @brody_mcwilliams, @froggtoggs, and @realtreeoutdoors. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Nothing screams that you’re fishing the Great Lakes more than wearing a rain suit on a bluebird day and big ole smallmouth! 🌊 🎣 @froggtoggs @froggtoggsfish

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jacob Wheeler on September 04, 2021.

node.text: Bites were not easy to come by but the quality on Lake Erie today was absolutely unbelievable! One of my top bags ever! Swipe to check out some of the pics. 🔥

node.text: Made it back up north a couple days early to get things dialed in before the last event of the season. We picked up right were we left off. Catching these Smallmouth never gets old! @igloocoolers

node.text: PSA: Whenever @adrianavenaprofishing and @jmartinduckman hop in the boat, things get WILD 😂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jacob Wheeler on August 27, 2021 tagging @academy, and @toyotausa. May be an image of 1 person, standing and body of water.

node.text: One week away from driving the @toyotausa Tundra north for the last event of the season on Lake St Clair! I’m ready to go battle some waves and reel in a few more smallmouth to close this season out in style. 😎

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jacob Wheeler on August 26, 2021 tagging @jmartinduckman. May be an image of 2 people and body of water.

node.text: Happy birthday to my brother from another mother @jmartinduckman! I’ve learned so many things about life, god and family from you and I’m truly grateful to call you a friend. Hope you have a great day J-Marty!
